This is a straightforward port of Joe Armstongs Wiki code (14.0) with
some minor extensions for having file attached to a page.

The pico-11.0 http server has been replaced 


To Install
----------

Edit include.mk then 

make
make install


Edit your /etc/yaws.conf and include /var/yaws/ebin in the
ebin path
	
    ebin_dir = /var/yaws/ebin

It is possible to have several Wiki instances on the same server. 
Just install the www/* files in the directory where you want a 
Wiki instance.

